'''Outlaws of Love'''（[[译名|译名]]：'''''禁忌的爱'''''、'''''爱的囚徒'''''或'''''爱的亡命之徒'''''）是[[美国|美国]][[犹太|犹太]][[歌手|歌手]][[亚当·兰伯特|亚当·兰伯特]]（{{lang|en|Adam Lambert}}）于2012年5月15日发行的一首[[英文|英文]]歌曲，单曲全长3分钟51秒，被收录于亚当·兰伯特的Trespassing专辑中的第十二首，是该专辑的特别单曲<ref>{{cite web|title=Global Superstar Adam Lambert To Release Highly Anticipated Second Album 'Trespassing' On March 20th, 2012 |url=http://www.rcarecords.com/news/global-superstar-adam-lambert-release-highly-anticipated-second-album-trespassing-march-20th-20 |work=RCA Records |publisher=RCA Records |date=2011-12-15 |accessdate=2011-12-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107185320/http://www.rcarecords.com/news/global-superstar-adam-lambert-release-highly-anticipated-second-album-trespassing-march-20th-20 |archivedate=2012-01-07 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Lansky, Sam|title=Adam Lambert's Sophomore Album, 'Trespassing,' Will Be Amazing. Here's Why|date=2011-12-08|accessdate=2012-03-26|url=http://buzzworthy.mtv.com/2011/12/08/adam-lambert-trespassing/?xrs=share_twitter}}</ref>。这首歌是亚当·兰伯特以自身的背景，写出和讲述关于自己身为男[[同性恋|同性恋]]不容于世的悲哀<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/reality-rocks/adam-lambert-discusses-gay-rights-anthem-outlaws-love-211304468.html |author=Parker, Lyndsey |title=Adam Lambert Discusses Gay Rights Anthem "Outlaws Of Love" |date=2012-05-10 |accessdate=2012-10-10}}</ref>，歌曲旋律以及歌词哀伤动人。<ref>{{cite|title=[心情] 歌曲分享 Adam Lambert- Outlaws of Love - All_Music板 - Disp BBS|url=https://disp.cc/b/942-7Lg1}}</ref>

